# Digital Resume

## 📌 About the Project
This project is a Digital Resume developed to present my professional profile, academic background, and technical skills in a modern and accessible way. Replacing traditional static files, this web version allows for a more dynamic and interactive experience for recruiters and collaborators

## 🚀 Features
- Clean & Professional Design
- Responsive Layout
- Section Organization
- Interactive Links

## 🛠️ Technologies Used 
- HTML5
- CSS3
- PHP

